#

Honey Garlic Glazed Salmon

$18.5
450 kcal
Difficulty: 30%

Allergens:

Fish

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeDairy-FreePaleo

Tags:

SeafoodEasyQuick

Description

A sweet and savory salmon dish with a luscious honey garlic glaze served over a bed of fluffy jasmine rice.

Ingredients

  • Salmon fillets: 2 (6 oz)
  • Honey: 3 tablespoons
  • Soy sauce: 2 tablespoons
  • Garlic cloves: 3, minced
  • Olive oil: 1 tablespoon
  • Lemon juice: 2 tablespoons
  • Salt: to taste
  • Pepper: to taste
  • Jasmine rice: 1 cup
  • Green onions: for garnish
